HEADWORD: Acquiescent
<hw>Ac`qui*es"cent</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>acquiescens</ets>, <ets>-centis</ets>; p. pr.]</ety> <def>Resting
satisfied or submissive; disposed tacitly to submit; assentive; <as>as,
an <ex>acquiescent</ex> policy</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Acquiescently</ent>⟦br⟧
